{"tid":524874,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[IOS] 睇下大家部iPhone電池壽命","createTime":"2018-01-10T05:12:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-14T11:30:27.000Z","uid":17245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b4ebd1f9819cfb027c3eb768df5862b7870ebce9","tid":524874,"uid":17245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T05:12:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/10/131005_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F10%2F131005_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=fbb29fe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\niPhone 自從6s 電既quality 好似差左<br />\n16年11月尾用到依家<br />\n340 cycle 已經扣左我7% 電容量<br />\n<br />\n以前部5S 500 cycle 先開始減percentage"},{"pid":"82db51c7b1294e189c0e4fdfee11c61387baa482","tid":524874,"uid":17245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T05:14:40.000Z","msg":"iOS 原生不支援電池監察功能，因此想監察電池狀態的話，就要以 Lightning 線將 iPhone 連接至 Windows PC 或 Mac 裝置上，再用監察程式查詢。<br />\n<br />\nCoconut Battery：Mac 免費電池監控 App<br />\n <br />\n正式使用 iPhone，但又因 iOS 禁止 App 報導電池循環使用數據，而擔心手機表現的話，Mac 用家可以下載免費 App《Coconut Battery》，再將 iOS 裝置經 Lightning 埠連接，就可以在 Mac 機上閱讀各種電池數據。現時《Coconut Battery》最新版本為 3.6.4，已能辨識 iOS 11 版本的裝置，及 iPhone10,（iPhone 8）與 iPhone10,2（iPhone 8 Plus）等裝置。<br />\n<br />\niBackupBot：PC 檢查 iOS 裝置工具<br />\n <br />\n使用 PC 平台的話，要檢測 iOS 裝置電池，雖然未像 Mac 有免費 App 可選，但仍有由 <a href=\"http://Copybot.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FCopybot.com&d=jv5VVIV7ClBSI%2BGCvZSj9QHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=1a7297d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Copybot.com</a> 推出的《iBackupBot》Free Trail 版本供試用。現時最新為 5.5.3 版本的《iBackupBot》Windows 版，對應主流 Win 10／8／7 的 64bit、32bit 版本，使用方式亦和上面《Coconut Battery》接近，都是連接 iOS 裝置後再啟動程式，勾選裝置名稱進入裝置頁面，再點擊「More Informations」查閱電池情況。"},{"pid":"28120969e602a070fc03402b7451eca24b6eb975","tid":524874,"uid":10904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T05:17:20.000Z","msg":"&lt;key&gt;com.apple.snapshot.battery.maxCapacity&lt;/key&gt;<br />\n  &lt;integer&gt;1700&lt;/integer&gt;<br />\n<br />\niPhone SE"},{"pid":"d6a151ae2768e0bf6822a59df6e10cfccfb843a6","tid":524874,"uid":1403,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T05:27:32.000Z","msg":"1399/1690<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前年八月買 都算係咁"},{"pid":"29558074f9368b490c8b34f158cc95ccf1ce55ce","tid":524874,"uid":27597,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T05:31:18.000Z","msg":"今朝起身13%, 差左一陣就54%<br />\n又用到兩個幾鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f29028fc2cd190cbbee56ad769f269d2ddd45407","tid":524874,"uid":15348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T05:37:06.000Z","msg":"1400/1715<br />\n16年10月買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706f9947b4af0c6a643c46e31ddeddfbe4fa6281","tid":524874,"uid":36356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T06:06:50.000Z","msg":"1200 / 1690"},{"pid":"5fcb78c34564c344a27a9929eea9b17a732d382d","tid":524874,"uid":11549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T10:27:55.000Z","msg":"CycleCount: 298<br />\n DesignCapacity: 2890<br />\n FullChargeCapacity: 2700<br />\n BatteryCurrentCapacity: 81<br />\n<br />\n用左14個月7plus <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44daea2b8e61c03322575162cdc075b50649129d","tid":524874,"uid":15348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fcb78c34564c344a27a9929eea9b17a732d382d","tid":524874,"uid":11549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T10:27:55.000Z","msg":"CycleCount: 298<br />\n DesignCapacity: 2890<br />\n FullChargeCapacity: 2700<br />\n BatteryCurrentCapacity: 81<br />\n<br />\n用左14個月7plus <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T13:18:08.0